1. *Velike* količine vode su potrebne za navodnjavanje. (Large amounts of water are required for irrigation.)

2. On je imao *veliki* uspeh na ispitu. (He had great success on the exam.)

3. On je imao *veliku* samouverenost. (He had great confidence.)

4. Ova zemlja ima *veliku* istoriju. (This country has a great history.)

5. Ona nosi *velikim* koracima. (She strides with large steps.)

6. On je stvorio *velike* promene. (He created great changes.)